to search for information on the types of lines and their application in drawing (thick and thin continuous, dashed, and chain).\ndraw various types of lines (thick and thin continuous, dashed and chain)\nsketch basic symbols (0, t, R, .l, □) and abbreviations (DRG, AIF, AIC, I/D, O/D) used in drawing\nuse audio-visual aids to study the application of symbols and abbreviations in drawing.', '', 'Drawing charts\nDrawing papers/books\nbrochures and magazines\nGeometrical set', 'Question and Answer\nObservation\nWritten Test\nPeer and Self-Assessment', '', '2026-04-12 12:35:58', '2026-04-12 12:35:58', NULL),
